Cell.Data: (iii) AVERAGE TAX RATES ON ANNUAL EARNINGS IN % TERMS*
* Average Tax Rates: Total of Income Tax, Levies and PRSI as a proportion of gross income. This measure includes only the standard
employee and personal income tax credits. It does not include the impact of any other allowances or reliefs.
** The Married two-Incomes figures assume that the joint income is divided 65% and 35% between spouses.
